{"tid":178242,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"我強烈建議辦公室茶水間要增設關愛爐","createTime":"2017-03-29T11:47:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T12:54:18.000Z","uid":6581,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"06036bb3045c3d37643558e534dc9147e4380c44","tid":178242,"uid":6581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:47:55.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我今日帶咗盒用玻璃盒裝嘅飯返工食<br />\n諗住健康啲就用蒸爐翻熱<br />\n點知蒸蒸下有個阿嬸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就大叫：「盒飯邊個嘅？！」<br />\n嗰時我嘅反應係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你個盒可以叮㗎喎，點解要蒸？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：（我依然俾唔到反應）<br />\n同事A：（解圍mode)咁蒸係好味啲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你要蒸就早啲或者遲啲先蒸，依家我要用，我個盒淨係可以蒸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：⋯⋯（我惟有黑住面拎走盒飯）<br />\n最過份嘅係我拎完盒飯去叮，返到嚟佢已經收埋咗個蒸爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇嚟呢個世界已經冇嘢可以阻到啲阿婆恃老賣老<br />\n所以我建議辦公室茶水間要增設關愛爐<br />\n等佢地唔使同我呢啲廢青爭爐用"},{"pid":"9098532964b97c38e7eea693fbdfdb37a1a6643c","tid":178242,"uid":6581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:55:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b737a49e50bba71d5b9085c2bfe03c5a6364832","tid":178242,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:56:34.000Z","msg":"屌鳩佢排隊囉 <br />\n和合石都要排啦"},{"pid":"dd658f798005d097047b137c0baa50e4aa38fd87","tid":178242,"uid":6581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:07:23.000Z","msg":"<bloc